The paper discusses the application of machine learning techniques to improve information retrieval in the domain of mathematics. This falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Natural Language Processing (cs.CL). The paper also explores the use of text embedding techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning for tasks such as language modeling and classification, indicating the relevance of Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL) to the topic.
